pulses.name: 20250110 Most Active Threat Indicators
pulses.description:
10 Jan 2025 : Most Active Threat Indicators
#Cybersecurity #Cyberattack #RCE #Botnet #IOC

Top 3 Source Countries:

- United States (US) - The US is a prominent source of cyber activities, with numerous instances of application layer scanning, backdoor traffic, and various attacks targeting web applications.
- China (CN) - China shows a high frequency of attacks, particularly involving remote code execution vulnerabilities in GPON routers and hardcoded passwords in web cameras.
- India (IN) - India is notable for multiple attacks targeting routers and devices, especially involving command injections and remote code execution vulnerabilities.
